## 2.4 Assessment (Legistlative Process)
[TOC]

### The Creation of a Bill
Either the House of Representatives or the Senate will introduce the idea of a bill<sup>1</sup>.

### Committee Action
Committees will organise subcommittees within itself to investigate the bill and reccomend the best course of action. This revision of the bill could include things such as hearings of experts or tabling the bill itself.

## Vocab
1. Bill - a potential law in progress
2. Tabling - laying the bill aside













